OL,3,CWrexham is most rewarding professional
OL,4,Cexperience of my life, says Reynolds
OL,6,FHollywood star Ryan Reynolds has made
OL,7,Fhis debut performance as a football
OL,8,Fcommentator, describing taking on
OL,9,FWrexham with actor Rob Mac as the
OL,10,F"most rewarding professional
OL,11,Fexperience of my entire life".
OL,13,FReynolds and Mac, who bought the north
OL,14,FWales club five years ago, commentated
OL,15,Fthe coverage of the game against
OL,16,FSwansea in the Championship on Sky
OL,17,FSports Football on Friday 13, March.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@]O]
