OL,3,CWrexham is most rewarding professional
OL,4,Cexperience of my life, says Reynolds
OL,6,FLive From Wrexham With Rob & Ryan saw
OL,7,Fthe pair discuss their passion for the
OL,8,Fteam ` and also divulge that they
OL,9,Fspoke to David Beckham on a video call
OL,10,Fduring Wrexham's match against Chelsea
OL,11,Flast weekend.
OL,13,F"We do a lot of FaceTime during the
OL,14,Fgame. So, in fact, during the Chelsea
OL,15,Fgame, David Beckham was FaceTiming
OL,16,Fwith us," Mac told the programme.
