OL,3,CWrexham is most rewarding professional
OL,4,Cexperience of my life, says Reynolds
OL,6,FAsked how they were feeling as the
OL,7,Fcoverage kicked off, Reynolds said:
OL,8,F"Nervous, nervous. As I said earlier,
OL,9,Fmost of what I know about commentating
OL,10,Flive sports is from old episodes of
OL,11,FProject Runway. So I am in big trouble
OL,12,Ftonight."
OL,14,FDiscussing how they came to buy
OL,15,FWrexham for around #2 million in 2021
OL,16,F` and have gone on to transform it `
OL,17,FMac said: "I Googled, how do I buy a
OL,18,Ffootball team?"
OL,20,FHe added: "It really got supercharged
OL,21,Fwhen Ryan got involved.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@IO]yD@KOUzD@OO]|D@KOU
