OL,3,CWrexham is most rewarding professional
OL,4,Cexperience of my life, says Reynolds
OL,6,F"And it went from probably a small,
OL,7,Ffun project into something that became
OL,8,Fa global phenomenon."
OL,10,FReynolds, whose actress wife Blake
OL,11,FLively attends many of the club's
OL,12,Fgames with him, said the team is a
OL,13,F"story that will never end".
OL,15,FHe continued: "It's been, easily for
OL,16,Fme, I'll say, the most rewarding
OL,17,Fprofessional experience of my entire
OL,18,Flife, and emotional, too.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]uD@AOUuD@[O]wD@OOU
