PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773504676
OL,3,CWrexham is most rewarding professional
OL,4,Cexperience of my life, says Reynolds
OL,6,F"Aside from my immediate nuclear
OL,7,Ffamily, I can't think of anything I've
OL,8,Fdone in my life that's more worthwhile
OL,9,Fand beautiful than being a part of
OL,10,Fthis story in Wrexham as it unfolds."
OL,12,FAs the game went on, the pair punched
OL,13,Fthe air and cheered as their team
OL,14,Fscored during the first half.
OL,16,FAnd they celebrated again when a
OL,17,Fsecond goal was scored, with Wrexham
OL,18,Fwinning the game 2-0.
