OL,3,CWrexham is most rewarding professional
OL,4,Cexperience of my life, says Reynolds
OL,6,FDrop It Like It's Hot by Snoop Dogg `
OL,7,FSwansea's co-owner ` was played across
OL,8,Fthe stadium at the final whistle.
OL,10,FReynolds and Mac have already made
OL,11,FEnglish football history with Wrexham
OL,12,Fachieving three consecutive
OL,13,Fpromotions, taking them from non-
OL,14,Fleague football to the Championship.
OL,16,FTheir progress has been documented in
OL,17,Fthe popular series Welcome To Wrexham,
OL,18,Fwhich has won 10 Emmy Awards and put
OL,19,Fthe club in the global spotlight.
