OL,6,FFeedback on their football
OL,7,Fcommentating skills was mixed on X,
OL,8,Fwith one user writing: "I wasn't gonna
OL,9,Flisten to it but I'm actually quite
OL,10,Fenjoying it."
OL,12,FAnother said: "This format is way
OL,13,Fbetter than regular commentary."
OL,15,FHowever another wrote: "Don't get me
OL,16,Fwrong, I don't mind these two but who
OL,17,Fthought this was a good idea."
